<p>Inshuti nyanshuti ntabwo ituma uhemuka<br />
Ikugira utunama two kwiyubaha<br />
Ukubaha uwo mubano utaretse iyakuremye<br />
Ikwigisha gukunda no kwifasha cyane ngo ujye imbere</p>

